< Rule 19 - The 12-question variant for weight loss
< When the user answers Pl= Ba jardepeso, thequestionnaire switches to its 12-question variant. The variant:
< Replaces PlO with P10-WL, with options specific to a weight-loss profile (includes GLP-1, bariatric surgery, ongoing medical care, pregnancy, hypertension, diabetes).
< Adds P11-WL • Current physical data - a screen with three numeric inputs in a single question: weight (kg), height (cm), age.
< Adds P12-WL • Change goal - single-select with options expressed as kilo ranges, no clinical absolutes.
< Shows a health disclaimer modal before presenting the result, with the signature of the medical reviewer backing the content.
< The full variant is 12 questions: Pl, P2, P3, P4, PS, P6, P7, PB, P9, PlO-WL, Pll-WL, P12-WL.
